com.akvelon.server.service.impl

Class SuperService<V extends Entity<java.lang.Integer>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.akvelon.server.service.impl.SuperService<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - type of domain object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service<java.lang.Integer,V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProductCategoryServiceImpl, ProductModelServiceImpl, ProductReviewServiceImpl, ProductServiceImpl, ProductSubcategoryServiceImpl

    @Service
public class SuperService<V extends Entity<java.lang.Integer>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Service<java.lang.Integer,V>
    Implementation of the Service interface. The class implements all CRUD operations for domain objects through DAO objects, whose ID type is Integer. Child classes must implement one abstract method from Service interface.
